article_title: Former U.S. attorney enters 2nd Congressional District race

article_metadata.description: Former U.S. Attorney Ken Sukhia is entering the Republican race for the 2nd Congressional District in a bid to unseat Democratic incumbent Rep. Gwen Graham.
article_metadata.author: ERYN DION
